---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now - Eric Huang"
  description="What I'm currently working on and interested in."
>
  <section class="layout-container">
    <div class="prose-custom">
      <h2 class="heading-2">What I'm Doing Now</h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        Last updated: <time>November 2025</time>
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-black">Work</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        Currently studying mathematics and computer science at Oxford. Working
        on building this website and exploring ideas in AI alignment and
        rationality.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-black">Learning</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        Diving deep into web development with Astro and Svelte. Exploring
        functional programming, type theory, and how to write better software.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-black">Reading</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-700">
        <li>Your favorite book here</li>
        <li>Another great book</li>
        <li>Essays and articles on LessWrong and various blogs</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-black">Thinking About</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        How to make better decisions, build meaningful projects, and contribute
        to solving important problems. Also pondering the nature of
        intelligence, consciousness, and what it means to live well.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-sm italic text-neutral-500">
        Inspired by <a
          href="https://nownownow.com/about"
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Derek Sivers' now page</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
